                                        </head_sticky><br />
                                        <para>
                                            No. Children are the future leader of this planet.<br /><br />
                                            Encouraging the concept of “think globally, act locally” is the first step for children to save our planet by saving electricity at home.
                                        </para>
                                    </alpha>
                                </li>





                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>




                </div>
            </form>
